{"tid":1163802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係我，你會詐唔知定踢爆佢？","createTime":"2019-05-20T16:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T16:29:19.000Z","uid":431,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7b44350842cee640755f232883f021bde4a220","tid":1163802,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:03:01.000Z","msg":"520係我同男朋友嘅一個月紀念日，所以約咗去食飯慶祝<br />\n我無要求佢送咩禮物畀我，但佢份人乜都要威，就送咗個lv袋畀我（雖然一齊得一個月但佢已經送過幾次名牌嘢畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身都唔好依啲...）<br />\n<br />\n之前我都無話post相上instagram曬命，但見佢話今日咁特別我就順下佢意post咗個story話多謝bb啊520快樂💓咁啦<br />\n點知個frd一見到我張相就話個袋係假嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柒到我即刻delete咗張相勁想搵窿損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先同個frd研究，原來唔單止個袋！連佢之前送畀我嗰幾樣都係a貨！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底我應唔應該踢爆佢無錢又扮嘢定詐唔知道算？<br />\n我覺得好唔開心...<br />\n點解佢會覺得我係要送名牌𠱁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係想同佢開開心心食餐飯..."},{"pid":"ce86528b586b1d89e2cd46925704f1b0c87d8d73","tid":1163802,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"入嚟為咗睇gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你竟然一個都冇"},{"pid":"da979a71f27732b6c72c8b6ead2c1d041d8c041d","tid":1163802,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce86528b586b1d89e2cd46925704f1b0c87d8d73","tid":1163802,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"入嚟為咗睇gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你竟然一個都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8d53c06a1808b7120e3412ebca21190cf65014","tid":1163802,"uid":38915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"ee